node.text:
👋🏽 Hey fam - I just got our new @honest_beauty Clean Conscious Culture kit and I am obsesssseeed! 🥰 S/o to the best team for working so hard and killing it ❗️ We’ve really stepped up our game when it comes to sustainability 🌱and this glow up ✨fully tells our story + values as a #cleanbeauty brand. 

This was my first time seeing the kit IRL and I wanted to go through it with my daughter Honor (better known as Honorcita 😜) who inspired me to create @honest. Check out the vid to see her blind reaction - and let me know your thoughts! Peace ✌🏽 Hugs 💗

**Always check with your local municipality for recyclability acceptance 🌍

node.text:
Havie my baby boo

My little 🦁 Leo ♌️ princessa. You are officially double digits 😩… although I know this day would come and I see you growing up before my eyes -I can’t help but get emotional just thinking about how fast it goes. We were in the car the other day and you said “Mom in 10 yrs from now, I’m gonna be 20 and you’re basically going to be the same but I’m gonna be an adult.” It’s just aggressive to talk about these things, I burst into tears every time. My soul aches for some reason… I wish we could pause on our days so we can get a few more hrs that I can just stare at you and take your sweet soul in. 

You have grown into a really cool kid- you were born with swag and a sense of self that take most people their whole life journey to get to. You have a way of making every room shine bright with your light. You cuddle hard, feel all the feels and express yourself with fervor always. Your laugh is everything✨you can turn someone’s day/mood around in an instant. You are a gift to me and to everyone around you boo. Hone in on your goodness, connect it with your keen intuition and intelligence, baby girl nothing in this life will be out of your reach. I’m proud of how kind and loving you are. Your joy and desire to have fun makes for no dull moments. 🥳! Thank you for choosing me to be your mommy. What a treasure you are my sweet baby Havie.

When I had the idea to create @honest (over a decade ago 🤯), I wanted to focus on the health and safety of people, but also #MotherEarth ♻️ From day 1️⃣, we’ve focused on product efficacy, formula integrity & ingredient quality - packaging is the next step in our journey of constantly trying to do better and be better. 

After many years in the works, I’m beyond stoked for @honest_beauty’s glow up ✨ - one that represents our values as a brand and our vision for the future. Clean. Conscious. Culture.™️ Where we care about people 👫🏽 and the planet 🌏 - all day, every day. Everything and everyone has been considered. Because that’s what we’ve always, and will always be about ❣️

Safe ingredients that really work 💯 Made with sustainability in mind 🌱 Showing the world that wellness is for everyone 👫🏽👩🏻‍🤝‍👨🏿👩🏼‍🤝‍👨🏻 It’s more than a moment. It’s a movement - to inspire everyone to love living consciously. Come join us 💚#CleanConsciousCulture #PeopleAndThePlanet

node.text:
Happy #InternationalWomensDay! 💗💗 This year’s theme is all about choosing to challenge. We’re all responsible for our own thoughts and actions all day, every day - and we should be choosing to empower women and smash stereotypes ‼️ Did you know 73% of women experience bias at work? Totally not acceptable. Did you know that only 37 companies in the Fortune 500 are run by women? Or, did you know that only 34% of Fortune 500 board seats are held by women and minorities? This needs to change.

Clearly, we’ve all got a lot of work to do. At The Honest Company, we’re determined to continue supporting our female workforce so that they feel safe and empowered - both professionally and personally. 68% of our workforce are women and 59% of our leadership team are women - women are at the core of everything we do! 👊🏽👊🏽

This year, I wanted to challenge myself, my @honest + @honest_beauty fam & YOU to call out gender bias and inequity when you see it. Join us as we #ChooseToChallenge ✋🏽 #IWD2021 #IWD

#TutorialTuesday - It’s so important to remember to take care of yourself, whatever way you see fit. For me, it’s all about the little things, like my sweet Hayesie Boo helping me make my fave matcha morning smoothie 💚 It’s super quick + easy and only includes 5 ingredients. Plus, the clean up is so simple, even a 3-year-old can handle it 🙌🏽🎉

INGREDIENTS: 
12 oz. Coconut Water - @harmlessharvest 
1 tbsp Almond Macadamia Be Well Blend - @wild_friends x @bewellbykelly
1 tsp Matcha Powder - @aiyamatcha
1 Whole Peeled Banana 
1 scoop Vanilla Grass-Fed Beef Protein Powder - @bewellbykelly 

DIRECTIONS: 
Add all of your ingredients into your blender and get it goin’! @blendtec 
Add about cup of ice to your mixture + blend together 
& your smoothie is ready to enjoy! 
Last step - some easy clean up @honest

node.text:
Havie my baby boo

My little 🦁 Leo ♌️ princessa. You are officially double digits 😩… although I know this day would come and I see you growing up before my eyes -I can’t help but get emotional just thinking about how fast it goes. We were in the car the other day and you said “Mom in 10 yrs from now, I’m gonna be 20 and you’re basically going to be the same but I’m gonna be an adult.” It’s just aggressive to talk about these things, I burst into tears every time. My soul aches for some reason… I wish we could pause on our days so we can get a few more hrs that I can just stare at you and take your sweet soul in. 

You have grown into a really cool kid- you were born with swag and a sense of self that take most people their whole life journey to get to. You have a way of making every room shine bright with your light. You cuddle hard, feel all the feels and express yourself with fervor always. Your laugh is everything✨you can turn someone’s day/mood around in an instant. You are a gift to me and to everyone around you boo. Hone in on your goodness, connect it with your keen intuition and intelligence, baby girl nothing in this life will be out of your reach. I’m proud of how kind and loving you are. Your joy and desire to have fun makes for no dull moments. 🥳! Thank you for choosing me to be your mommy. What a treasure you are my sweet baby Havie.

node.text:
This week for #WCW I’m featuring none other than the ultra-philanthropic, always chic (never in sweats, unless they’re mine 😂), #BFF for life @kellysawyer ❣️

Right around the time I was starting @honest, Kelly and her co-President Norah joined @baby2baby - a nonprofit dedicated to providing essential items to families in need with children 12 years and under 💚.  In the last 10 years, Baby2Baby.org has grown from a local LA charity taking gently used items and redistributing to children in need -to becoming the largest diaper bank in the US, shows up for global disaster relief and has been key in getting the diaper tax bill passed. @baby2baby has donated over 175 million items with huge initiatives around diapering needs, safe sleep needs, nutrition needs and hygiene needs for so many families in the US‼️ Kell, I am always in awe of everything you do for others & all the ways you take care of not just those who are closest to you- your family and friends but of course, all the babies, kiddos and parents you give hope to. You have a heart of gold and your relentless positive attitude is an integral part of how you tackle some of the most pressing and difficult challenges with grace.

Whether we are eating all the food🍝 (enjoying a few adult beverages 🤷🏽‍♀️), having impromptu back yard dance parties, traveling to fashion week or family vacays, getting in a workout💪🏽, double date nights👯‍♀️, having babies, celebrating birthdays and anniversaries - it's always the best times w you 💃🏼 You are the Thelma to my Louise, the Wilma to my Betty, the Mark to my Juno - my #RideOrDie - cheers to the memories we have created and to so many more yet to come! I love you ❤️ 

To my Insta fam - if you are able to give back in any way, through time, money, and/or items, I strongly encourage you to join us. Please make sure to follow @baby2baby or visit Baby2Baby.org to learn how you can support the ongoing relief efforts 🙏🏽. If we all do a little something, we can change the course of so many peoples lives for the better. 🥰
